<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>èr shí yī shì jì de zhōng guó 迦南852</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 èr shí yī shì jì de zhōng guó, shì zuì dà de fú yīn hé chǎng.
 shén yǐ jiāng tā de xīn yì, fàng zài le wǒ men de jiān shàng.
 jī dū de jīng bīng, huì jù zài shì jiè dōng fāng.
 tīng cóng yé sū de hū zhào, yào bǎ fú yīn chuán biàn sì fāng.
 juān juān xiǎo liú yǐ liú rù jiāng hé, jiāng hé jǐ huì rù hǎi yáng.
 yé hé huá xíng qí shì, shéi néng lái zǔ dǎng. quán de zhèng zài xiàng tā gē chàng.
 léi shēng shì jūn gǔ, tiān shǐ yě zài dà hé chàng.
 zuì dà de fú yīn hé chǎng shì zhōng guó, zhǔ de róng guāng yǐ zhào liàng dōng fāng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>852</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>